h1 {
  line-height: 1.15;
}
Try values in this range:

1.1 → very tight

1.15 → ideal for headings

1.25 → normal heading spacing

Avoid normal for large fonts.


this inn tailwind
Why Tailwind doesn’t include 1.15 by default

Tailwind ships typographic-safe values:

leading-none → 1

leading-tight → 1.25

leading-snug → 1.375

leading-normal → 1.5

1.15 is design-specific, so Tailwind expects you to define it.